        "content": "<p>Here's a formal statement, FYI:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Mathlib.Analysis.Calculus.ContDiff.Defs</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Mathlib.MeasureTheory.Integral.IntervalIntegral</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Mathlib.Analysis.Calculus.Deriv.Basic</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span> <span class=\"n\">BigOperators</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">funCoe</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Ï†</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">â„</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’</span> <span class=\"n\">â„‚</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">â„¤</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’</span> <span class=\"n\">â„‚</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"k\">fun</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†¦</span> <span class=\"n\">Ï†</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span>\n\n<span class=\"sd\">/-- ** Partial summation ** -/</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">theorem</span> <span class=\"n\">sum_eq_int_deriv</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Ï†</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">â„</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’</span> <span class=\"n\">â„‚</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">â„</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Ï†Diff</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ContDiffOn</span> <span class=\"n\">â„</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span> <span class=\"n\">Ï†</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Set.Icc</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">))</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Finset.Icc</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">âŒŠ</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"bp\">âŒ‹</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">âŒŠ</span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"bp\">âŒ‹</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sum</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">funCoe</span> <span class=\"n\">Ï†</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">âˆ«</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"k\">in</span> <span class=\"n\">a..b</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Ï†</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">âŒŠ</span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"bp\">âŒ‹</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span> <span class=\"bp\">/</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">Ï†</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">âŒŠ</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"bp\">âŒ‹</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span> <span class=\"bp\">/</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">Ï†</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span>\n      <span class=\"bp\">-</span> <span class=\"bp\">âˆ«</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"k\">in</span> <span class=\"n\">a..b</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">âŒŠ</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">âŒ‹</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span> <span class=\"bp\">/</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">deriv</span> <span class=\"n\">Ï†</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n  <span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Of course <code>exact?</code> doesn't work, so I'm guessing the answer is No?</p>",
