        "content": "<p>Also (and this may be related to the ongoing L-series discussion...), is there a better way to implement that <code>funCoe</code>? Why doesn't Lean know that if I have a function <code>â„ â†’ â„‚</code> but I'm looking for a function <code>â„¤ â†’ â„‚</code>, I can compose with the coercion <code>â„¤ â†’ â„</code>...?</p>",
